centurymetadata-ai-experimental-client
=======================================

An interactive learning client for the centurymetadata protocol
(https://centurymetadata.org) by Rusty Russell.

This is an experimental / proof-of-concept project. It is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or officially connected to the upstream centurymetadata project.
For production use, refer to the reference implementation at
https://github.com/rustyrussell/centurymetadata.

Attribution
-----------
The encode/decode logic in src/lib/centurymetadata.ts is a TypeScript port of
Rusty Russell's Python reference implementation
(https://github.com/rustyrussell/centurymetadata/tree/master/python),
adapted to use browser-compatible libraries. See LICENSE for the full
third-party notice and per-file provenance comments in the source for the
specific upstream file each function derives from.

Test vectors in test/unit-tests.mjs are derived from the standard BIP-39
"abandon abandon ... about" public test mnemonic and the upstream
test_vectors.json. No real wallet material is present in this repository.

